## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **zolbetuximab Vyloy 2024** = first FDA claudin-18.2 mAb 1L gastric + GEJ HER2-negative. SPOTLIGHT + GLOW pivotal Phase 3. claudin-18.2 (CLDN18.2) 가 위상피세포 tight junction 특이적 → tumor 표적 narrow window. quantum-VQE 의 tight junction transmembrane epitope modeling 이 직접 fit.
2. **T-DXd trastuzumab deruxtecan Enhertu 2021 gastric + 2024 expansion** = first FDA HER2+ gastric ADC. DESTINY-Gastric01 + 04 + 06 expansion. HER2-low subset 도 expanding. trastuzumab 2010 ToGA 후 13년 만의 HER2 axis advance. quantum-VQE 의 ADC linker + DXd payload modeling.
3. **pembrolizumab + nivolumab 2017 → 2021 1L + chemo paradigm shift** = MSI-H gastric (2%) → HER2- 전체 1L IO + chemo. KEYNOTE-859 + CheckMate 649. PD-L1 CPS≥1 vs CPS≥5 cutoff 임상 controversy.
4. **imatinib Gleevec 2002 GIST → ripretinib 2020 + avapritinib 2020 (PDGFRA D842V)** = GIST 5세대 KIT/PDGFRA TKI evolution. switch-control + allosteric. quantum-VQE 의 KIT exon 11/13/17 + PDGFRA D842V mutational fitness landscape 가 fit.
5. **vonoprazan PCAB Voquezna 2022** = first FDA potassium-competitive acid blocker — PPI alternative + H. pylori eradication 향상. CYP2C19 polymorphism 무관. 한국 + 일본 K-pharma 강한 분야 (cross-k_pharma_industry).
6. **H. pylori 만성 + 만성 macrolide-resistant 호발 한국 + 일본** = quad therapy + bismuth + vonoprazan combo. 만성 위암 1차예방 paradigm. cross-microbiome 강한 link.
7. **EBV-positive gastric (10%) + MSI-H gastric (5-15%)** = molecular subgroup TCGA 2014 분류. EBV+ → IO + EBV oncolytic 후보. MSI-H → IO + checkpoint 효과 강함.
8. **HDGC CDH1 cross-inherited_adult** = familial diffuse gastric — prophylactic gastrectomy 권고. CDH1 germline mutation. cross-link `.roadmap.disease_inherited_adult`.
9. **K-gastric cancer 임상 framework** = 한국 위암 발생률 OECD 1위 + 식약처 산정특례 + 국가검진 위내시경 40+ 2년 1회. 한국형 임상 framework 강한 fit (cross-k_pharma_industry).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, esophageal + gastric + GEJ + GIST 임상 의미 한정.

